@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mgabni(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.cos(wp.abs(v2 + 0.62)))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.exp((v2 + 0.95 + v0 + 0.18)))
    tmp = 0.13
    v2 = v1
    v1 = wp.sin((wp.abs(v1 + 0.26) + (v2 + 0.96 / v1 + 0.39)))
    tmp = wp.cos(0.53)
    tmp = v2
    tmp = v0
    data[tid] = v0
